  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the fermented chwinamul and soak it in water for 30 minutes.",
    "Drain and chop the chwinamul into small pieces.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the turmeric, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Add the basmati rice and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and stir in the bonito flakes.",
    "Serve the pilaf hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
